title: Highest Net ODA Provided
description: In 2017, Sweden provided net official development assistance (ODA) totaling 1.02% of its Gross National Income (GNI), one of the highest contributions globally.

title: Lowest Particulate Emission Damage
description: In 2021, Sweden had one of the lowest particulate emission damages, accounting for only 0.009% of its GNI.

title: High School Enrollment for Males
description: In 2015, Sweden achieved a high net enrollment rate for males in secondary education at 99.81%.
